  <div id="open-igloo">
    <h2>Open Your Igloo </h2>
	
	<div align="right">
      <table width="100%"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="10">
        <tr>
          <td valign="top"><ul>
              <li class="plaintext"> If you are a member, you can open your igloo to other players. This means they can come and visit you, even if they are not on your buddy list. </li>
              <li class="plaintext"> When you are in your igloo, if you would like other players to visit you, click on the lock icon on the right side. This will &ldquo;open&rdquo; your igloo to other players by adding it to the map. </li>
              <li class="plaintext"> If you want to visit another player&rsquo;s igloo, open the map, click on the igloo, and select the name of a penguin who you would like to visit. </li>
              <li class="plaintext"><FONT face=Arial><SPAN 
style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">To close your igloo, click the lock again. If you log out, your igloo is automatically locked again.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT><FONT face=Arial><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></li>
              <li class="plaintext"> You can always visit a buddy&rsquo;s igloo, even when they are not online. Simply open your buddy list, select their name to bring up the player card, and then click on the house icon.</li>
          </ul></td>
          <td valign="top"><p><img src="../../../images/screenshots/open-igloo.gif" width="350" height="220"></p></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <p><a href="#" onClick="return goAnchor('top')">        Back to top</a> </p>
