      <div id="play-music">
        <h2>How to Play Music </h2>
        <div align="right">
          <table width="100%"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="10">
            <tr>
              <td valign="top" class="plaintext"><ul>
                  <li>To play music in your igloo, you first need something to play music with, like the Jukebox or Home Stereo.</li>
                  <li>If you own either of these items, click on the tape measure at the bottom right when you&rsquo;re in your igloo. This allows you to edit your igloo. </li>
                  <li> Once you&rsquo;re in Edit mode, if your Jukebox or Home Stereo is already in your igloo, a cassette tape icon will appear on the right. </li>
                  <li>If your Jukebox or Home Stereo is in storage, you still cannot play the music. To place the items in your igloo and out of storage, click on the box icon, and then click on the Jukebox or Home Stereo. Then click in your igloo where you want to place it. </li>
                  <li>You should now see the cassette tape icon. Once that icon is visible, click it. </li>
                  <li> This will open the Music List. Click on the song you want to play! </li>
                  <li>To turn the music off, open the Music List again, and click &ldquo;No Music&rdquo;. </li>
                  <li>Remember to click the tape measure again to get out of edit mode. </li>
                </ul>
                  <p>If you would like to play music but you do not own the Juke Box or Home Stereo:</p>
                  <ul>
                    <li>First click the tape measure; </li>
                    <li>Then the blue catalog to buy either item. </li>
              </ul></td>
              <td valign="top"><table width="100%"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                    <tr>
                      <td><img src="../../../images/screenshots/music1.gif" width="350" height="220"></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td><img src="../../../images/screenshots/music2.gif" width="350" height="220"></td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>                  <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
            </tr>
          </table>
          <p><a href="#" onClick="return goAnchor('top')">        Back to top</a>          </p>
